children.name: Rules
children.text:
This blue scaled scabbard is made from the thick leather hide of a deadly marlin, and bits of its natural sharp bill are woven into the leather. 
This scabbard can be used to sheath any dagger, shortsword, longsword, rapier, scimitar, or great sword. Once per session, as a bonus action used to draw the blade from the scabbard, the welder gains the following bonuses until the start of their next turn. 
+1 AC
+20 Speed
+2 Damage
